<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>오렌지 키우기 게임</title>
  <link rel = "stylesheet" href = "/css/index.css">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="game-frame">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="title">
        <div class="orange-icon">🍊</div>
        <h1>Oh! Range, Orange</h1>
        <p class="subtitle">가장 큰 오렌지를 만들어보세요!</p>
      </div>

      <div class="menu">
        <a href="/game" class="menu-button start">게임 시작</a>
        <button class="menu-button" onclick="openModal('optionsModal')">옵션</button>
        <button class="menu-button" onclick="openModal('creditsModal')">제작자 정보</button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="optionsModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <button class="close-button" onclick="closeModal('optionsModal')">&times;</button>
      <h2>⚙️ 옵션</h2>
      
      <div class="option-item">
        <label>사운드 효과</label>
        <div class="toggle-switch active" onclick="toggleOption(this)"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="option-item">
        <label>배경 음악</label>
        <div class="toggle-switch active" onclick="toggleOption(this)"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="option-item">
        <label>진동 피드백</label>
        <div class="toggle-switch" onclick="toggleOption(this)"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div id="creditsModal" class="modal">
    <div class="modal-content">
      <button class="close-button" onclick="closeModal('creditsModal')">&times;</button>
      <h2>👨‍💻 제작자 정보</h2>
      <p><strong>게임 이름:</strong> Oh! Range Orange</p>
      <p><strong>개발:</strong> jynoh00</p>
      <p><strong>버전:</strong> 1.0.0</p>
      <p><strong>설명:</strong> 가장 큰 오렌지를 키우는 타이밍 게임입니다</p>
      <p><strong>배포 년도:</strong> 2025</p>
      <a href = "https://github.com/jynoh00">https://github.com/jynoh00</a>
    </div>
  </div>
  <script type = "text/javascript" src = "/js/index.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
